title: The Deep End
description:
Today, we're diving into the deep end. First, Sapphire shares a story about the mythical Kelpie. Then, guest storyteller Andrew Tate (host of the Let's Not Meet Podcast) reads a story from a hotel security guard, who had a strange run-in at the pool. Then, Sapphire and Andrew have a chat about his podcast, as well as dive into some existential theories.
